cs" rel="category tag">Politics</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/rttv" title="View all posts in RTTV" rel="category tag">RTTV</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/spies" title="View all posts in Spies" rel="category tag">Spies</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/syria" title="View all posts in Syria" rel="category tag">Syria</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/terrorism" title="View all posts in Terrorism" rel="category tag">Terrorism</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/un" title="View all posts in UN" rel="category tag">UN</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/war-2" title="View all posts in War" rel="category tag">War</a>			</span>
