				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-cat-links">Posted in</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/civil-liberties" title="View all posts in Civil Liberties" rel="category tag">Civil Liberties</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/current-affairs" title="View all posts in Current Affairs" rel="category tag">Current Affairs</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/drugs-2" title="View all posts in Drugs" rel="category tag">Drugs</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/economics" title="View all posts in Economics" rel="category tag">Economics</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/law" title="View all posts in Law" rel="category tag">Law</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/leap" title="View all posts in LEAP" rel="category tag">LEAP</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/police" title="View all posts in Police" rel="category tag">Police</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/politics" title="View all posts in Politics" rel="category tag">Politics</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/ssdp" title="View all posts in SSDP" rel="category tag">SSDP</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/talks-2" title="View all posts in Talks" rel="category tag">Talks</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/uncategorized" title="View all posts in Uncategorized" rel="category tag">Uncategorized</a>			</span>
									<span class="sep"> | </span>
							<span class="tag-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/leap" rel="tag">LEAP</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/prohibition" rel="tag">prohibition</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/ssdp" rel="tag">SSDP</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/war-on-drugs" rel="tag">war on drugs</a>			</span>
						
